                          GrabBag links)
        Creates a PottsCellFlyNeuron PottsCell agent. Population links provided in constructor are not used because this cell type does not divide. This constructor allows for all constructor calls in PottsCellContainer to have the same format.
        Parameters:
        container - the cell container
        location - the Location of the cell
        parameters - the dictionary of parameters
        links - the map of population links
